            "heading": "SHIPPING & DELIVERY",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We deliver <strong>worldwide</strong>, so you can enjoy Momplush wherever life takes you, effortlessly.</p><ul><li><strong>Free Worldwide Delivery</strong> – No minimum order</li><li><strong>Tracked Shipping</strong> – Follow your order every step of the way</li><li><strong>Processing Time</strong> – Orders are prepared within 1–2 business days<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Estimated delivery times:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Europe</strong>: up to 5 business days</li><li><strong>North America</strong>: up to 10–15 business days</li><li><strong>South America</strong>: up to 20–25 business days</li><li><strong>Middle East</strong>: up to 15–20 business days</li><li><strong>Asia</strong>: up to 15–23 business days</li><li><strong>Africa</strong>: up to 20–25 business days<br/></li></ul><p>Please note: Delivery times may vary slightly during peak periods or due to customs delays.</p>",
            "page": "",
